    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the available evidence across all thirteen factors and determined that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient credibility for the intended VAD use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds were considered adequate, and the overall body of evidence was judged to support acceptance of the model predictions for regulatory submission purposes.",
